---
description: Use English source text as i18n keys in frontend code
globs: apps/frontend/src/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Frontend i18n Keys

- When calling `t(...)`, use the exact English source text as the key.
- Do not introduce semantic ids like `authErrorTitle`, `profileButtonLogin`, or similar.
- Do not use `defaultValue` to avoid adding a real translation key.
- If the English phrase is new, add it to `apps/frontend/src/i18n/languages/en.json` with the same text as both key and value.
- Add the same key to every locale file in `apps/frontend/src/i18n/languages/`.
- Keep interpolation in the English key itself, for example: `t("Round #{{roundId}} completed", { roundId })`.
